        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Preventing Racial Profiling in Lending Act </strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits a federal agency from requiring any person or entity to estimate a borrower's race or ethnicity through visual observation or surname when extending credit. </p>]]></text>
